00:28:06.460 --> 00:28:08.190
as I'd meet these players.

00:28:08.190 --> 00:28:10.150
Joe Cooley was an amazing
man to meet.

00:28:10.150 --> 00:28:13.390
He would take the time to talk
to a child, and I was only 11

00:28:13.390 --> 00:28:16.010
when I met him and it really
had a big effect on me.

00:28:16.010 --> 00:28:19.060
But most of the guys were just
young and there would be beer

00:28:19.060 --> 00:28:23.480
and a few shots and that would
be a little crazy and they did.

